        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row no-gutters">
        <div class="col-lg-6 text-white showcase-img" style="background-image: url('startbootstrap-landing-page-gh-pages/img/bg-showcase-2.jpg');"></div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 my-auto showcase-text">
          <h2>International Law</h2>
          <p class="lead mb-0">Newly improved, and full of great utility classes, Bootstrap 4 is leading the way in mobile responsive web development! All of the themes on Start Bootstrap are now using Bootstrap 4!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row no-gutters">
        <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2 text-white showcase-img" style="background-image: url('startbootstrap-landing-page-gh-pages/img/bg-showcase-3.jpg');"></div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1 my-auto showcase-text">
          <h2>Künstliche Intelligenz</h2>
